data.description: Home is in a peaceful established neighborhood in central Brownsville. This home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a spacious living room area with vaulted ceiling, open kitchen with dining area, spacious and fenced big back yard, backyard patio area, 2 car garage, central air conditioning, and tile flooring throughout. Master bathroom was recently remodeled and a new air condition unit was recently installed. Private entrance to bathroom was added to bedroom 2. Stove, refrigerator, and over the stove microwave included. No HOA fees.  The home is within 3 minutes of Expressway 83, within 5 minutes of local shopping centers like Sunrise Mall and Target, within minutes of grocery stores and restaurants like Olive Garden and Cheddar’s, and only 35 minutes away from South Padre Island. Easy to show.
data.whatILove: Quiet area with peaceful neighborhood. Near expressway 83 and shopping centers. Located in the middle of Brownsville, Texas.
